{"title":"老农的脊梁","authors":["赵贵辰"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":1,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"老农的脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵贵辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮肤黄土色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裸着一面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黝黑的脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风刮　就刮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨打　就打"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反正摧残不了一畦苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面栽种着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫倔强"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进哪块土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪块土地就肥沃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在什么地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么地方就芬芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一座碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座活动的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民纪念碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请读那脊梁吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么碑文能比上？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}